buidler-introduction.title: Buidler Introduction
buidler-introduction.description: Buidler is a messaging platform lets you dive into communities right on the sites you're browsing, instantly. By installing the Buidler Extension, you can hang out, ask questions, or collaborate with everyone on the website directly on your browser - without switching or searching for chat channels.

install-live-chat-plugin.title: Install Live Chat Plugin
install-live-chat-plugin.description: By enabling Buidler Live Chat on your website, you can provide your visitors with an easy way to get in touch with you and receive real-time support.
